quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  2,197,"Hajju ngun (hajju oo):ko lebbi anndaaЙ—i. Mo anniyike he nder majji hajju,renndugol he debbo alaa,wanaa faasoqingol wanaa kadi yeddondiro ka hajju.Kala ko mbaЙ—-Й—on he moЖґЖґere Alla (Geno) na anndi Й—um .YooЙ“ee (njooЙ“o-Й—ee),ko Й“uri moЖґЖґude he njooЙ“a, ko deentol. Hulee Lam joomiraaЙ“e hakkillaaji."
  2,198,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde Й—aЙ“Й“oton arsike immorde he Joomi mon. Si on iwtii 'Aarafaat, JaЕ‹tee innde Alla ka nokku horminannde. NjaЕ‹te-Й—ee mo wano (hono) no o feewniri on nii, hari on laatinooma ado ko on jeyaaЙ“e he majjuЙ“e."
  2,199,"Refti yahron ka yimЙ“e Й“en yahri Й—on, Imsino-Й—on Й—o Alla. Pellet Alla ko YaafotooЙ—o jurmotooЙ—o."
  2,200,"Si on gaynii dewe hajju mon ngun, njaЕ‹to-Й—ee innde Alla wano no njaЕ‹torton baabiraaЙ“e mon, maa ko Й“uri Й—uum tiiЙ—ude. No woodi he yimЙ“e Й“en wi'ooЙ“e: "Joomi amen rokku men ka aduna", alanaa mo ka (to) laakara geЙ—al moЖґЖґal."
  2,201,"No he maЙ“Й“e wi'ooЙ“e: Joomi amen, okku min moЖґЖґere aduna e laakara, ndanndaa min lebte jayngol"
  2,202,"ЖЃen (Й“een) Й—oon, no woodani Й“e geЙ—al moЖґЖґal he ko Й“e faggitii. Alla ko YaawuЙ—o hasboore"